## Oracle Linux 6u7
Download "V77197-01.iso Oracle Linux Release 6 Update 7 for x86_64 (64 Bit)"
from Oracle Software Delivery Cloud and place the file V77197-01.iso in this folder


## CDR Tools

Download the latest version of cdrtools (cdrtools-3.*.tar.gz) from 
http://sourceforge.net/projects/cdrtools/files/

Build cdrtools, instructions below have been tested on OS X and may vary 
per host operating system. For detailed information see http://cdrecord.org or 
http://sourceforge.net/projects/cdrtoolswin/

	mkdir cdrtools
	tar -xf cdrtools-3.*.tar.gz -C cdrtools
	cd cdrtools
	cd cdrtools*
	make









